<h1>JLPT N2 grammar list</h1>


		<div class="light">You can also check out <a href="/jlpt/jlpt2/grammar/usage/">N2 grammar usage</a>. (Taken from Kanzen Master.)</div><br />
		
<div class="light">This is not a cumulative list. (It doesn't contain the grammar needed by JLPT N3 and below). <a href="combined/">Click here for a cumulative list</a>.</div><br />
